data.description: Welcome to this charming 1930’s Spanish style home in Los Angeles. This home features 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and a detached garage.     As you enter the home, you’ll notice the large living room with high, coved ceilings adding elegance and character to the property. You can fully enjoy the warmth and ambiance of your fireplace while creating an inviting space for relaxation. The open concept living room connects to the dining room and cozy family room. Adjacent to the dining room is the kitchen with an eating area and inside laundry.     Other notable features include a carport and long driveway leading to the garage with an adjacent storage shed for additional storage. Create an inviting outdoor space with the backyard’s large concrete patio area.     This property is just a short drive to SoFi Stadium, the KIA Forum, LAX, major freeways and many more points of interest. Make this charming home yours today!
